  "name": "Quantum Brick",
  "mood": "Aether",
  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "Harmonic wavetable into FM (fmDepth 0.45) into Wavefolder (proc1) — the maximum complexity chain available in OBRIX. The Harmonic bank provides a dense partial structure which FM then cross-modulates into non-linear territory, and the Wavefolder then folds those combined partials back onto themselves. Three stages of harmonic multiplication produce timbres that have no name in traditional synthesis vocabulary. proc2=LP at 8000 Hz preserves the result without killing the air. Env→wtPos means each attack sweeps through a different quantum state.",
